casebody.data:
Ellen FORREST, Respondent,
v.
CHILDREN'S HOSPITALS & CLINICS OF MINNESOTA, Relator, BRAC, Administrator,
and
Summit Orthopedics, Intervenor. A18-1499 Supreme Court of Minnesota. January 8, 2019 Dana Gerber, Atkinson Law Office, Saint Paul, Minnesota, for respondent. Edward Cassidy, Fredrikson & Byron, P.A., Minneapolis, Minnesota, for relator. Considered and decided by the court without oral argument.

ORDER

Based upon all the files, records, and proceedings herein,

IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that the decision of the Workers' Compensation Court of Appeals, filed on August 16, 2018, be, and the same is, affirmed without opinion. See Hoff v. Kempton , 317 N.W.2d 361 , 366 (Minn. 1982) ("Summary affirmances have no precedential value because they do not commit the court to any particular point of view," doing no more than establishing the law of the case).

Respondent is awarded attorney fees in the amount of $3,500.

BY THE COURT:

/s/ ______________________________

David L. Lillehaug

Associate Justice
